citation: Proclamation under the Taxi and Luxury Hire Car Industries Amendment Act 2009 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Taxi and Luxury Hire Car Industries Amendment Act 2009

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Taxi and Luxury Hire Car Industries Amendment Act 2009 fix 1 January 2010 as the day on which that Act commences.

21 December 2009

PETER G. UNDERWOOD

Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

G. L. STURGES

Minister for Infrastructure

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 30 December 2009

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Infrastructure, Energy and Resources.
